WEBVTT

00:07.880 --> 00:10.800
THREE YEARS LATER, SPRING OF
THE 24TH YEAR OF CHENGPING'S REIGN

00:19.240 --> 00:20.640
Pirates! Pirates!

00:22.520 --> 00:25.760
Please spare us! They will kill us
if you steal everything away!

00:33.680 --> 00:35.600
Song Mo? This is a trap!

01:29.800 --> 01:30.640
Tell us.

01:31.520 --> 01:32.760
Where is your base?

01:37.880 --> 01:39.200
Song Mo,

01:39.280 --> 01:41.880
do you think capturing me
will lead you to our base?

01:41.960 --> 01:44.240
We people of Dongyu will never yield!

01:50.280 --> 01:51.320
Is it

01:51.880 --> 01:53.160
South Mountain?

01:54.880 --> 01:58.760
Tongzhou? Jilang? Zhanshui? Shan Island?

01:58.840 --> 02:00.480
Meizhou? Feiyu Island?

02:00.560 --> 02:02.240
Or Zhou Island?

02:07.280 --> 02:08.440
So it's in Zhou Island.

02:11.520 --> 02:14.960
Song Mo, you tricked me!
You won't get your way!

02:15.040 --> 02:16.200
General, it's all thanks
to your brilliance.

02:16.280 --> 02:19.480
Because of that darn rations
officer's delay, we nearly starved!

02:19.560 --> 02:22.440
-If you hadn't baited the pirates…
-Lu Ming, shut up.

02:22.520 --> 02:24.360
-…we'd still be starving.
-Stop! Get on your knees!

02:25.480 --> 02:27.280
General, my brother is new here.

02:27.360 --> 02:29.720
He doesn't know the rations officer
is your father, Duke of Ying.

02:29.800 --> 02:32.120
-Please forgive him.
-His anger is understandable.

02:32.200 --> 02:33.120
I'm angry too.

02:33.640 --> 02:35.840
If you want to complain, go ahead.
I won't hear a thing.

02:39.920 --> 02:41.280
At least we didn't ruin
Grand General's plan.

02:41.360 --> 02:44.080
Taking down five pirate ships
should count as a decent result.

02:44.800 --> 02:46.240
Five ships aren't enough.

02:48.960 --> 02:51.000
-Duke of Ding's Army, hear my command!
-Yes, General!

02:51.080 --> 02:53.440
Everyone, eat quickly.

02:53.520 --> 02:56.760
In half an hour, change into pirates'
clothes and head for Zhou Island.

02:57.680 --> 03:00.160
To secure ten years of peace
for the people of Futing,

03:00.240 --> 03:03.520
we must make history with this battle!

03:03.600 --> 03:06.320
For the homeland! For a place in history!

03:06.400 --> 03:08.640
For the homeland! For a place in history!

04:29.280 --> 04:32.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL BLOSSOM
BY AUTHOR ZIZI FROM QIDIAN CHINESE WEBSITE

04:36.200 --> 04:39.360
FUTING

04:46.760 --> 04:48.360
Attack! Attack!

04:48.880 --> 04:51.440
The Duke of Ding's Army will win!
The Duke of Ding's Army will win!

04:53.040 --> 04:54.200
Hey!

04:54.280 --> 04:55.320
It's the Duke of Ding's Army!

04:56.360 --> 05:02.440
-They're back!
-The Duke of Ding's Army is back!

05:04.240 --> 05:05.960
The Duke of Ding's Army is back!

05:06.480 --> 05:08.280
They're back!

05:15.440 --> 05:17.040
-Did you win?
-We did.

05:17.120 --> 05:18.200
A great victory at Zhou Island.

05:18.280 --> 05:20.680
With the sea now pacified,
the goods will become valuable again.

05:20.760 --> 05:21.920
That's great!

05:22.000 --> 05:23.440
Zheng, aren't we impressive?

05:24.360 --> 05:26.560
Don't be dramatic. This is nothing.

05:26.640 --> 05:27.920
There's more glory to come.

05:28.000 --> 05:30.720
-Long live the Duke of Ding's Army!
-The Duke of Ding's Army!

05:30.800 --> 05:32.040
All thanks to the Duke of Ding's Army!

05:32.560 --> 05:34.440
Lu Zheng, have the Ministry of War send

05:34.520 --> 05:36.280
the captured women
and children back to Dongyu.

05:36.360 --> 05:37.800
Any soldier found abusing children

05:37.880 --> 05:41.080
or assaulting women will be executed.

05:41.160 --> 05:42.320
Yes, General!

05:44.400 --> 05:45.480
Congratulations, General.

05:45.560 --> 05:47.800
News of your attack on Zhou Island

05:47.880 --> 05:48.840
has reached the camp.

05:49.680 --> 05:50.720
The Duke has also arrived.

05:51.600 --> 05:52.760
My father is here?

05:56.520 --> 05:57.720
Jiang Mei Sun!

05:58.360 --> 05:59.600
The delay in the delivery

05:59.680 --> 06:01.280
was because our troops
encountered bandits along the way.

06:01.360 --> 06:03.800
We were eliminating threats to
the people. How is that a crime?

06:04.320 --> 06:05.360
Release me!

06:05.920 --> 06:07.440
-Release me!
-Grand General.

06:07.520 --> 06:09.160
He's the Duke of Ying

06:09.680 --> 06:10.560
and your brother-in-law.

06:10.640 --> 06:12.120
Listen up, everyone!

06:12.640 --> 06:14.160
DING

06:14.240 --> 06:16.800
Song Yi Chun has delayed
military operations

06:18.280 --> 06:20.360
and spoken outrageously.

06:21.200 --> 06:22.400
As per military law,

06:22.920 --> 06:24.680
30 lashes.

06:25.200 --> 06:26.800
-Carry out the punishment.
-Yes, sir!

06:26.880 --> 06:28.400
How dare you! I am
a duke of the highest rank,

06:28.480 --> 06:29.640
with generations of merit behind me.

06:29.720 --> 06:32.040
Without an imperial decree,
who dares to touch me?

06:36.480 --> 06:37.520
Grand General!

06:51.880 --> 06:52.880
Yan Tang.

06:55.760 --> 06:58.320
Grand General, I have
completed the mission successfully.

06:58.400 --> 06:59.400
Please get up.

07:00.000 --> 07:01.320
Despite the shortage of rations,

07:01.400 --> 07:02.680
we managed to dismantle the Dongyu forces,

07:02.760 --> 07:04.200
thanks to you acting as bait.

07:04.280 --> 07:06.080
Well done! This is a great achievement.

07:06.800 --> 07:07.840
Grand General,

07:08.360 --> 07:10.280
not only did the General
destroy ten enemy ships,

07:10.360 --> 07:12.400
he also used their fleet
to seize Zhou Island.

07:12.480 --> 07:14.520
The last pirate stronghold
has been wiped out.

07:15.280 --> 07:17.440
The decades-long mission to
secure the borders and seas

07:17.520 --> 07:18.360
has finally succeeded.

07:18.440 --> 07:21.120
Bravo! Bravo!

07:24.600 --> 07:25.760
Oh, you…

07:25.840 --> 07:27.440
you were short on supplies

07:28.040 --> 07:29.160
and outnumbered.

07:29.240 --> 07:31.240
Were you trying to get yourself killed?

07:32.880 --> 07:34.680
It's thanks to the delay of the rations

07:34.760 --> 07:36.560
that my son had the drive
to fight against the odds.

07:37.440 --> 07:40.280
Yan Tang, reason with your uncle for me.

07:40.360 --> 07:41.840
I'm tired of arguing with him.

07:41.920 --> 07:42.760
How absurd!

07:43.560 --> 07:46.040
Discipline comes first in the army.
There's no room for family sentiment!

07:46.880 --> 07:49.240
You lost sight of the bigger picture,
chasing credit for taking out bandits

07:49.320 --> 07:50.640
and delaying the delivery by ten days!

07:50.720 --> 07:52.880
If Yan Tang hadn't taken the initiative,
we would have lost this battle!

07:52.960 --> 07:54.360
And you still dare to justify yourself?

07:54.440 --> 07:56.760
Bring me the whip!
I'll punish him personally!

07:56.840 --> 07:58.800
-You wouldn't dare!
-Watch me!

07:58.880 --> 08:02.200
Grand General, it's true
the Duke of Ying is guilty of delay,

08:02.720 --> 08:05.240
but doing nothing and watching
my aging father suffer punishment

08:05.920 --> 08:07.000
makes me an unfilial son.

08:08.120 --> 08:09.440
30 lashes would cripple him,

08:10.160 --> 08:11.000
if not kill him.

08:11.080 --> 08:13.000
I did nothing wrong!

08:13.960 --> 08:15.320
I beg you, Grand General!

08:15.960 --> 08:17.440
In light of the victory at Zhou Island,

08:18.200 --> 08:20.760
allow me to take his punishment.

08:21.280 --> 08:23.960
It upholds military law
and preserves loyalty and filial piety.

08:27.000 --> 08:28.440
Please show mercy, Grand General!

08:28.520 --> 08:30.640
Please show mercy, Grand General!

08:30.720 --> 08:32.679
Please show mercy, Grand General!

08:43.000 --> 08:45.240
Loyalty and filial piety, huh?

08:54.000 --> 08:55.000
Fine.

08:56.440 --> 08:57.280
As you wish then.

08:58.440 --> 09:00.160
You will take ten extra lashes.

09:01.880 --> 09:02.720
Do you accept it?

09:07.880 --> 09:08.880
Yes, sir!

09:10.240 --> 09:11.480
I'm sorry.

09:20.360 --> 09:21.320
Let's go!

09:22.160 --> 09:24.200
An outstanding son with a useless father.

09:25.880 --> 09:27.120
How foolish!

09:42.360 --> 09:43.200
This may hurt.

09:48.520 --> 09:49.680
Look at you,

09:50.480 --> 09:52.440
you dared to attack Zhou Island

09:52.520 --> 09:54.240
with only a few ships and troops.

09:54.760 --> 09:56.160
You were practically courting death.

09:56.680 --> 09:57.760
Reckless!

09:59.560 --> 10:00.640
The Art of War says,

10:02.160 --> 10:03.960
"Throw them into death ground,
and they will fight to survive;

10:04.040 --> 10:05.600
place them in peril, and they will thrive.

10:06.160 --> 10:07.640
Desperate troops always win."

10:08.480 --> 10:09.400
You taught me that.

10:12.720 --> 10:14.600
Don't throw war strategies at me.

10:15.400 --> 10:17.040
I may not have been there,

10:17.560 --> 10:19.400
but I know exactly what you were thinking.

10:20.120 --> 10:21.320
Your attack on Zhou Island

10:21.400 --> 10:24.200
was just to plead
for your father's pardon.

10:26.840 --> 10:28.600
And you saw how he repaid you.

10:28.680 --> 10:29.560
Was it worth it?

10:30.720 --> 10:32.280
Why did you have to whip him for real?

10:33.360 --> 10:34.480
I told him to.

10:35.000 --> 10:37.520
There's no jesting in the military.
Forty lashes are nothing.

10:37.600 --> 10:39.280
I said I'd take the punishment
for my father,

10:39.360 --> 10:40.800
so I had to bear it without pretense.

10:41.760 --> 10:44.280
-Leave us.
-Yes, sir!

10:47.880 --> 10:48.760
Uncle,

10:49.720 --> 10:51.880
worth it or not, he's my father.

10:51.960 --> 10:53.360
My mother and Han

10:53.880 --> 10:55.120
are waiting for him to come home.

10:57.480 --> 10:58.920
This is my fault.

10:59.000 --> 11:02.200
I should never have agreed
to let Hui Sun marry him.

11:03.720 --> 11:04.920
That's not fair.

11:05.920 --> 11:07.720
If they hadn't married, I wouldn't exist.

11:07.800 --> 11:10.120
And without me, who would keep
you company securing the borders?

11:10.200 --> 11:13.000
You'd be so bored. Honestly,

11:14.480 --> 11:17.520
I feel refreshed right now, like
after a good cupping treatment.

11:18.800 --> 11:21.000
You feel refreshed, huh?

11:26.440 --> 11:28.520
The Duke of Ying has packed up and left.

12:02.280 --> 12:04.120
FLOURISH

12:10.680 --> 12:11.800
Lighting every lamp,
burning every incense.

12:11.880 --> 12:13.240
Grain God,

12:13.320 --> 12:15.400
bless us with a bountiful harvest,

12:15.480 --> 12:18.200
and may Shou Gu and An Su
earn baskets full of money.

12:22.360 --> 12:24.000
Farmers pray for favorable conditions

12:24.080 --> 12:26.640
because they depend on
the weather to survive.

12:27.360 --> 12:29.240
But businesses rely on human effort.

12:29.840 --> 12:31.440
Instead of asking the gods,

12:31.960 --> 12:32.840
maybe you should reward me generously.

12:35.280 --> 12:36.280
Don't speak carelessly.

12:36.360 --> 12:38.600
Even launching ships for trade
depends on the heavens.

12:39.240 --> 12:41.320
Oh, Grain God,
don't hold it against Shou Gu.

12:41.400 --> 12:45.320
If you have time, please bless us
with more wealth and fortune.

12:46.680 --> 12:49.080
I predict the pirates will be
completely eradicated this year,

12:49.840 --> 12:51.960
and spring and summer trade
will bring great wealth.

12:52.040 --> 12:54.080
I'll make sure to add to your fortune.

12:54.880 --> 12:58.000
If you really are a clairvoyant,

12:58.600 --> 13:00.800
did you see this coming?

13:02.400 --> 13:03.440
Zhang Ru!

13:04.120 --> 13:06.000
Oh, I got another premonition.

13:06.080 --> 13:08.000
You won't find a husband this year either.

13:09.160 --> 13:10.840
How dare you say that!

13:12.240 --> 13:13.160
Zhang Ru!

13:26.560 --> 13:27.520
Good news!

13:27.600 --> 13:29.280
I've got great news!

13:31.120 --> 13:32.120
-Su Su.
-Su Su.

13:33.120 --> 13:34.640
What are you doing?

13:37.640 --> 13:38.960
What are you doing?

13:39.960 --> 13:41.000
Stop it!

13:43.320 --> 13:44.360
Stop!

13:49.880 --> 13:51.040
Oh, no.

13:51.120 --> 13:52.240
What are those?

13:52.320 --> 13:53.560
Money.

13:56.920 --> 13:59.000
You didn't guess it would be money.

14:00.120 --> 14:01.680
One thousand taels each,

14:01.760 --> 14:03.160
and so many of them!

14:03.240 --> 14:05.320
There aren't many
this wealthy in all of North Zhili.

14:05.400 --> 14:08.640
The tea, silk, and porcelain
we stocked last year

14:08.720 --> 14:09.800
all sold at a premium.

14:09.880 --> 14:11.600
Thanks to Zhao seizing
the opportunity early,

14:12.240 --> 14:13.480
my father says

14:13.560 --> 14:15.920
this month's shipping orders
have increased tenfold.

14:16.000 --> 14:17.800
The profits will only grow from here.

14:19.400 --> 14:22.280
An Su, go back and tell
Mister and Madam Miao

14:22.360 --> 14:25.560
to sell the ships after
selling off our current stocks.

14:26.080 --> 14:26.920
We'll look for a new business opportunity.

14:28.280 --> 14:31.280
-Shou Gu, are you serious?
-Why?

14:31.800 --> 14:33.800
We've established our business
in Futing early on

14:33.880 --> 14:35.600
and became the shipping tycoon here.

14:35.680 --> 14:38.800
When all the sea routes open up,

14:38.880 --> 14:40.440
won't we make even more money then?

14:40.520 --> 14:42.960
This is the 24th year
of the Chengping reign.

14:43.040 --> 14:45.360
The Duke of Ding's Army's coastal
campaigns are nearly finished.

14:45.880 --> 14:47.000
With the pirates eradicated,

14:47.520 --> 14:49.480
maritime trade will
become hugely profitable.

14:50.080 --> 14:52.520
From local officials in Futing
to the Ministry of Revenue,

14:53.040 --> 14:54.880
they're bound to tighten
regulations and increase taxes.

14:55.400 --> 14:57.200
This business might not
be as easy as it seems.

14:57.280 --> 15:00.120
Even if local officials
want to take a cut,

15:00.200 --> 15:01.920
it's not like the business
would become unviable.

15:02.000 --> 15:04.160
Isn't pulling out now too early?

15:04.680 --> 15:08.480
Or did you hear something from Mr. Chen?

15:08.560 --> 15:09.440
No, nothing like that.

15:09.960 --> 15:12.040
It's just that when you buy
during a slump,

15:12.120 --> 15:13.440
even if prices rise, it's still cheap;

15:13.520 --> 15:15.640
and when you sell during a boom,
even if prices fall, it's still high.

15:15.720 --> 15:17.840
If everyone knows it's easy money,

15:17.920 --> 15:19.120
then there's no real profit left.

15:19.640 --> 15:20.520
Trust me on this.

15:21.360 --> 15:23.360
I don't understand all that,
but I know one thing,

15:23.880 --> 15:25.520
If you become the richest person
in Zhending,

15:25.600 --> 15:28.560
your stepmother and
your fiance, Marquis of Jining,

15:28.640 --> 15:30.240
will be drooling counting your money.

15:30.320 --> 15:31.800
Young Lady Zhao,

15:32.400 --> 15:33.840
Nanny Zhou from the capital is here.

15:35.720 --> 15:37.440
Great, speak of the devil,

15:37.520 --> 15:39.160
and the devil appears.

15:39.240 --> 15:42.880
I've clearly turned down
the family banquet for the festival,

15:43.400 --> 15:44.960
and now they're inviting me again.

15:45.040 --> 15:47.720
I have distant relatives visiting,

15:47.800 --> 15:49.560
no time to play doting mother
to a happy family.

15:50.160 --> 15:53.520
Oh, Old Madam, how can
you say such a thing?

15:53.600 --> 15:55.880
It's rare for both Fifth Master and
Seventh Master to be here.

15:55.960 --> 15:59.760
A family reunion during the festival
is a wonderful thing!

16:00.600 --> 16:01.800
To be honest,

16:02.320 --> 16:05.000
Seventh Master caught
a cold a few days ago.

16:05.520 --> 16:06.960
He's been missing his daughter terribly.

16:08.720 --> 16:09.760
Using my father as an excuse?

16:09.840 --> 16:12.360
If I don't go, I'll be accused
of being unfilial, won't I?

16:13.480 --> 16:15.560
Young Lady Zhao,
how can you think that way?

16:15.640 --> 16:16.920
Madam went out of her way

16:17.000 --> 16:19.960
to prepare a whole table
of dishes just for you.

16:20.560 --> 16:23.000
Is her food even edible?

16:23.520 --> 16:25.480
Yes, what if she's up to no good

16:25.560 --> 16:28.000
and poisons the food?

16:28.520 --> 16:29.520
I refuse to believe she would be nice.

16:29.600 --> 16:31.600
How can you say such things?

16:32.440 --> 16:33.600
Fine.

16:34.960 --> 16:35.960
Shou Gu, are you really going?

16:38.520 --> 16:41.680
Grandmother, since Father still remembers
he has another daughter,

16:42.360 --> 16:43.200
I want to go.

16:43.280 --> 16:45.560
We're going with Zhao then.

16:45.640 --> 16:48.800
Surely you won't mind
receiving a few more guests.

16:50.560 --> 16:52.080
Alright then.

16:52.600 --> 16:55.400
The capital is only half a day's
journey from Zhending.

16:56.520 --> 16:57.840
Nanny Zhou,

16:58.520 --> 17:00.560
take good care of my granddaughters.

17:00.640 --> 17:02.280
Of course!

17:07.560 --> 17:08.720
Candied Hawthorn!

17:08.800 --> 17:09.640
I'd like one, please.

17:10.560 --> 17:12.040
DUKE OF YING'S RESIDENCE

17:41.160 --> 17:42.560
SONG HAN

17:46.080 --> 17:49.120
Han, your spear skills
have improved a lot.

17:49.200 --> 17:51.800
I imagine your mother has
worked hard to train you.

17:53.040 --> 17:54.440
Nonsense.

17:54.520 --> 17:56.080
It's been ages since
I practiced with a spear.

17:56.160 --> 17:58.400
A little exercise is good for me anyway.

18:05.520 --> 18:07.120
Brother? You're back!

18:08.120 --> 18:10.120
Yan Tang? Yan Tang!

18:12.280 --> 18:13.440
Mother.

18:15.640 --> 18:17.160
This is a dagger seized from the pirates.

18:17.800 --> 18:18.640
It's yours now.

18:20.880 --> 18:22.000
Thanks, Mo!

18:23.800 --> 18:26.560
I heard you were badly injured
in the battle at Zhou Island.

18:26.640 --> 18:27.480
Where are you hurt?

18:27.560 --> 18:30.040
-Let me take a look.
-I'm fine.

18:32.120 --> 18:34.520
After such a bumpy journey,
how could your body handle it?

18:35.880 --> 18:38.560
Showing off your big victory
the moment you walk in, huh?

18:39.560 --> 18:41.320
His uncle takes good care of him.

18:41.840 --> 18:43.280
He doesn't need us.

18:46.400 --> 18:48.000
Will you stop picking
fights with my brother?

18:48.080 --> 18:49.440
The children are watching.

18:54.480 --> 18:55.600
Ignore him.

18:57.040 --> 19:00.120
It's been a while since
you've tasted my cooking.

19:00.720 --> 19:01.680
Get some rest.

19:01.760 --> 19:03.760
I'll cook for us today.

19:03.840 --> 19:05.640
Let's have a family reunion dinner.

19:05.720 --> 19:07.800
Great! I'll help you in the kitchen.

19:07.880 --> 19:08.800
Alright.

19:17.000 --> 19:17.880
Leave us.

19:29.360 --> 19:31.120
Your uncle sure knows
how to play his cards.

19:31.200 --> 19:33.320
He submitted an expedited military report

19:34.040 --> 19:35.680
accusing me of negligence and delay,

19:35.760 --> 19:38.280
and only your merit
spared me from the lashes.

19:39.040 --> 19:41.640
Now the entire court knows!

19:41.720 --> 19:43.280
As a father,

19:43.360 --> 19:44.760
I had to rely on my excellent son

19:44.840 --> 19:47.000
and beg for Jiang Mei Sun's mercy.

19:47.960 --> 19:50.440
It's a victory report,
not an impeachment letter.

19:50.960 --> 19:53.600
Amid the joy of a great victory,
a few sentences mentioning this matter

19:54.120 --> 19:55.840
ensure His Majesty doesn't
dig deeply into your mistakes.

19:56.520 --> 19:58.600
Did I do wrong to eliminate
bandits for the people?

19:59.200 --> 20:00.800
If you hadn't volunteered for the lashes,

20:00.880 --> 20:02.960
I'd still have a case
to argue before His Majesty.

20:03.600 --> 20:04.880
Now this is great.

20:04.960 --> 20:08.000
His Majesty has demoted me to
overseeing the South City garrison.

20:08.520 --> 20:11.240
The son earns merit
while the father gets demoted.

20:11.320 --> 20:13.600
You still think Jiang Mei Sun
did this out of kindness?

20:13.680 --> 20:15.200
Father, this…

20:15.960 --> 20:17.920
So you do know I'm your father.

20:18.480 --> 20:19.320
For years,

20:19.920 --> 20:22.640
you've barely come home.

20:23.160 --> 20:25.040
His Majesty praises you

20:25.560 --> 20:27.400
for embodying Jiang Mei Sun's integrity.

20:28.280 --> 20:29.720
Now I'm confused.

20:30.320 --> 20:31.920
Whose son are you?

20:52.600 --> 20:53.520
Is it over there?

20:53.600 --> 20:55.400
-I'll buy one for you, alright?
-Yes.

21:03.400 --> 21:04.240
Do you like it?

21:10.040 --> 21:11.920
Whose son are you?

21:12.520 --> 21:16.120
His Grace has been strict
with you since you were little.

21:16.800 --> 21:18.240
Rules and expectations

21:18.800 --> 21:19.840
are naturally stricter in noble families.

21:24.880 --> 21:26.120
I've only just realized

21:26.640 --> 21:28.040
that during the years I've been away,

21:28.560 --> 21:29.520
my parents and brother

21:30.040 --> 21:32.120
have grown close, like a true family.

21:32.760 --> 21:33.840
My return

21:34.360 --> 21:36.120
has only disrupted their harmony.

21:40.800 --> 21:42.000
I'd like to take a walk alone.

21:42.520 --> 21:43.440
Don't follow me.

21:53.440 --> 21:54.760
Today,

21:54.840 --> 21:57.440
the shadow puppet show we'll perform

21:57.960 --> 22:00.600
is called The Record of Truths.

22:01.240 --> 22:03.400
-Yes!
-Yes!

22:33.040 --> 22:35.080
Would it be better for everyone

22:35.600 --> 22:37.880
if I weren't the heir to the Duke of Ying?

22:41.400 --> 22:44.720
Awesome!

23:07.080 --> 23:09.200
-Yes!
-Bravo!

23:22.320 --> 23:23.560
It's been so long
since I've been to the capital.

23:23.640 --> 23:24.880
The festival here is so lively!

23:24.960 --> 23:26.280
Look at all these Nuo opera masks!

23:26.360 --> 23:27.920
We're going to be late.

23:28.000 --> 23:29.800
Ladies, why did you
get off the carriage here?

23:29.880 --> 23:31.120
Fifth Master and
Seventh Master are waiting.

23:31.200 --> 23:33.600
Come on, get back in! Quickly!

23:46.960 --> 23:49.360
Ladies, I'll go inform
Fifth Master and Seventh Master.

23:51.600 --> 23:52.680
Young Lady Zhao.

23:56.960 --> 24:00.600
Chen Shi Yuan, Liu Xue Zhen,
Pang Kun Bai…

24:00.680 --> 24:03.640
All the guests are sons of
newly prominent court officials.

24:04.160 --> 24:05.520
Know your enemy

24:05.600 --> 24:07.160
and prepare accordingly.

24:09.720 --> 24:11.200
So many young men are here.

24:11.720 --> 24:14.520
If I'd known,
I would've dressed up properly!

24:14.600 --> 24:16.160
They're all Uncle Shi Shu's students,

24:16.240 --> 24:17.440
from prestigious families.

24:18.440 --> 24:19.720
They're celebrating their promotion.

24:19.800 --> 24:21.840
Our attire does seem inappropriate.

24:22.360 --> 24:23.480
Zhao.

24:26.520 --> 24:28.600
Zhao, what are you doing here?

24:32.640 --> 24:33.640
Ming, you look stunning.

24:36.120 --> 24:37.400
I simply did as Mother asked.

24:37.920 --> 24:40.000
I didn't know you'd be coming today.

24:43.640 --> 24:45.000
We have many guests today.

24:45.080 --> 24:48.640
Let's go to my room first and
get you all changed. Come on.

24:48.720 --> 24:49.880
-Zhao!
-It's fine…

24:50.440 --> 24:52.440
You're finally here.

24:52.520 --> 24:54.640
Master and Shi Shu are waiting for you.

24:55.160 --> 24:57.640
Ming, why didn't you
announce your sister's arrival?

24:59.000 --> 25:00.240
Come with me.

25:00.960 --> 25:01.880
This way.

25:07.400 --> 25:09.360
Master, Zhao and the girls are here.

25:09.440 --> 25:12.200
Not bad. They are all talented young men.

25:14.600 --> 25:15.480
Shou Gu.

25:17.800 --> 25:21.280
Our guests today
are all prominent figures.

25:21.360 --> 25:23.560
It's rude enough that you're late,

25:24.080 --> 25:25.280
and look at how you're dressed.

25:25.960 --> 25:26.960
Standing next to Ming,

25:27.680 --> 25:29.040
you look like a servant.

25:29.120 --> 25:30.720
Shou Gu dressed like her grandmother.

25:31.240 --> 25:32.080
Simple and elegant is perfectly fine.

25:33.040 --> 25:33.880
This is my fault.

25:34.480 --> 25:37.320
I should have reminded the girls.

25:37.840 --> 25:39.440
I'll take them to get changed now.

25:39.520 --> 25:40.360
PANG KUN BAI

25:40.440 --> 25:41.120
Come.

25:43.400 --> 25:46.480
Please forgive us, Uncle Shi Shu.
My sisters and I wore plain clothes

25:46.560 --> 25:47.840
not out of disrespect,

25:47.920 --> 25:50.440
but because dressing extravagantly
felt inappropriate.

25:52.160 --> 25:53.000
How so?

25:53.080 --> 25:56.120
Disasters have struck
across the land since last year,

25:56.200 --> 25:57.080
and wars have been frequent.

25:57.160 --> 26:01.080
His and Her Majesties have cut back
on their use of jewels and silks,

26:01.160 --> 26:03.440
urging officials not
to indulge in extravagance.

26:04.200 --> 26:05.440
I hear you are set

26:05.520 --> 26:07.320
to be promoted in the Ministry of Rites.

26:07.400 --> 26:09.480
With the promotion decree not yet issued,

26:09.560 --> 26:10.960
such a grand display might invite

26:11.560 --> 26:13.200
criticism from your political rivals.

26:13.280 --> 26:14.480
Well…

26:15.360 --> 26:16.680
You're right.

26:17.200 --> 26:19.280
I hadn't considered that.

26:19.360 --> 26:20.200
This is a festive occasion!

26:20.280 --> 26:23.080
Even common folk dress brightly

26:23.160 --> 26:24.360
for good fortune.

26:24.440 --> 26:27.400
Zhao, must you always tie
everything back to national affairs?

26:27.480 --> 26:29.320
It's rare to hear

26:29.400 --> 26:31.160
such practical and grounded insights

26:31.240 --> 26:32.600
from a noble lady.

26:35.600 --> 26:36.960
Who is he?

26:38.480 --> 26:39.600
As expected of you, Young Lady Zhao.

26:43.720 --> 26:46.120
Young Master Wu, it's been a while.

26:46.200 --> 26:47.680
How is Lord Wu?

26:47.760 --> 26:49.160
My grandfather is in good health.

26:49.240 --> 26:52.160
On his behalf, I extend
early congratulations to you,

26:52.680 --> 26:53.840
-Fifth Master and Seventh Master.
-Thank you.

27:03.360 --> 27:05.800
-Young Master Wu, this way, please.
-Remove the lanterns.

27:05.880 --> 27:08.360
Ying Xue, take Ming to change into
something more suitable.

27:16.520 --> 27:19.200
Wu Shan, the only grandson
of Grand Secretary Wu.

27:20.200 --> 27:22.240
I didn't know you had a connection
with the Wu family.

27:23.120 --> 27:25.280
My stepmother is an expert at networking.

27:25.920 --> 27:28.200
Besides, Wang Xing Yi is Wu Shan's mentor.

27:28.800 --> 27:31.600
At this banquet, he's likely the arrow,

27:32.160 --> 27:35.200
and either Dou Ming or I
will be the target.

27:41.920 --> 27:42.840
They're actually changing the lanterns?

27:42.920 --> 27:44.760
Mr. Chen, your prediction became true.

27:44.840 --> 27:47.080
You even knew they would change
the lanterns during the banquet.

27:47.720 --> 27:49.280
Since they're changing the lanterns,

27:49.800 --> 27:52.440
it means Young Lady Zhao
and the girls are not only safe

27:54.280 --> 27:56.000
but may have even gained an advantage.

27:58.760 --> 28:00.000
Let's go, Mother.

28:00.080 --> 28:01.080
Ming, let me ask you,

28:01.720 --> 28:04.800
what were you and Dou Zhao
talking about at the door earlier?

28:06.720 --> 28:09.200
I was just catching up with my sister.

28:09.280 --> 28:11.240
She's never treated you as a sister,

28:11.320 --> 28:14.640
yet you're eager to call her one.

28:15.360 --> 28:17.400
Everything I'm doing is for your own good.

28:17.480 --> 28:20.840
Why do you think I went to all that
trouble inviting Young Master Wu here?

28:20.920 --> 28:22.600
But I don't have feelings
for Young Master Wu…

28:22.680 --> 28:23.960
Enough!

28:24.520 --> 28:26.000
When it comes to choosing a husband,

28:26.080 --> 28:28.200
your feelings are the least important.

28:29.640 --> 28:31.640
Young Master Wu comes
from an esteemed family.

28:32.160 --> 28:33.440
He's kind and ambitious.

28:33.960 --> 28:35.680
There's no better match.

28:37.920 --> 28:39.640
You've just come of age

28:39.720 --> 28:40.960
at the height of your beauty.

28:41.040 --> 28:42.440
Tonight,

28:42.520 --> 28:44.800
you must make me proud, understand?

28:46.280 --> 28:47.640
-Yes, Mother.
-Let's go.

28:56.200 --> 28:57.200
Shou Gu.

29:01.880 --> 29:04.600
The discussion about politics earlier
was just a cover.

29:05.640 --> 29:06.680
I'm dressing plainly

29:07.200 --> 29:09.320
because Mother's death anniversary
is approaching.

29:10.200 --> 29:11.960
Do you remember that?

29:13.040 --> 29:14.520
Of course I do.

29:16.800 --> 29:18.040
Look at this magnolia tree.

29:18.560 --> 29:21.200
I tend to it personally.

29:21.720 --> 29:24.200
It's blooming especially well this year.

29:25.120 --> 29:26.400
Flowers bloom again,

29:26.480 --> 29:27.680
but the dead cannot return.

29:29.200 --> 29:31.880
The celebration is
just an excuse, isn't it?

29:31.960 --> 29:33.560
You and Uncle Shi Shu are using

29:33.640 --> 29:35.680
this opportunity to parade
our family's daughters

29:35.760 --> 29:38.680
in front of Young Master Wu
and the other guests, aren't you?

29:40.520 --> 29:43.840
Your uncle is just concerned
about your marriage prospects.

29:45.000 --> 29:46.760
Am I supposed to lower myself to scrutiny

29:46.840 --> 29:50.080
and competition with Ming, like a
peacock spreading its tail?

29:50.600 --> 29:51.920
The elders mean well.

29:52.440 --> 29:53.520
Don't look at it so negatively.

29:54.160 --> 29:56.520
Back then, Uncle Shi Shu
insisted you marry Wang Ying Xue

29:57.120 --> 29:58.720
to gain the Wang family's support.

29:59.240 --> 30:01.160
Now that he's risen from a clerk
at the Office of Transmission

30:01.240 --> 30:02.680
to a senior post in the Ministry of Rites,

30:02.760 --> 30:04.680
does he really need to use our marriages

30:04.760 --> 30:05.800
to curry favor with the Wu family?

30:06.440 --> 30:07.360
Dou Zhao,

30:07.960 --> 30:09.720
you shouldn't slander your elders.

30:10.480 --> 30:12.280
Marriage has always been
decided by the parents.

30:12.360 --> 30:14.680
-Have I ever forced you into anything?
-You may not have forced me,

30:14.760 --> 30:15.680
but you've never raised me either.

30:16.320 --> 30:18.440
Keeping things simple and staying out
of each other's way suit us just fine.

30:18.520 --> 30:20.360
-You…
-As for your high hopes,

30:20.440 --> 30:21.680
place them on Ming instead.

30:21.760 --> 30:23.040
When she marries,

30:23.560 --> 30:24.880
I'll contribute to her dowry.

30:32.520 --> 30:35.000
Young Lady Ming seems delicate.
It makes me want to protect her.

30:35.720 --> 30:36.920
But she doesn't look like
she's built for childbearing.

30:37.000 --> 30:39.960
Young Lady Ming is reserved
for Young Master Wu,

30:40.040 --> 30:41.280
so don't bother trying.

30:41.360 --> 30:43.320
If you want to rely on the Dou family,

30:43.920 --> 30:47.880
aim lower, at someone they've written off,

30:47.960 --> 30:48.800
like that girl from the Zhao family.

30:49.520 --> 30:50.640
I might as well marry
Young Lady Zhao then.

30:51.320 --> 30:54.160
-At least she's filthy rich.
-Young Lady Zhao is mine.

30:54.240 --> 30:55.440
You can have Young Lady Miao instead.

30:56.240 --> 30:58.240
Her family may not be as wealthy,

30:58.320 --> 31:00.520
but at least she's easy to control.

31:01.040 --> 31:02.880
A gentleman knows to exercise
restraint in his words and actions.

31:02.960 --> 31:05.600
Yet here you are, under their roof,
engaging in such vile discussions.

31:05.680 --> 31:08.680
Have all the moral lessons
you've studied been for nothing?

31:17.360 --> 31:20.200
Trust me, pick Young Lady Miao.

31:20.280 --> 31:21.240
Just trust me.

31:26.600 --> 31:28.160
What is this?

31:28.240 --> 31:29.640
It stinks!

31:35.480 --> 31:37.520
This is a rain gauge
from the Ministry of Works,

31:37.600 --> 31:39.640
used by various provinces to
measure rainfall and prevent disasters.

31:39.720 --> 31:40.800
It must not be tampered with.

31:50.640 --> 31:52.040
Ming is here.

31:57.840 --> 31:59.400
The star of the show is here.

31:59.480 --> 32:01.000
Should we just play supporting roles?

32:01.080 --> 32:03.080
Yes, keep quiet and stay out of sight.

32:03.160 --> 32:04.640
Just focus on eating and drinking.

32:05.160 --> 32:06.720
I agree with that!

32:07.320 --> 32:09.560
Everyone, it's a pleasure
to have you here.

32:09.640 --> 32:11.080
Please make yourselves at home. Here.

32:11.160 --> 32:12.200
-Zhao.
-Here.

32:17.680 --> 32:19.680
Gentlemen, you are
all well-learned scholars.

32:19.760 --> 32:20.920
I have a suggestion.

32:21.440 --> 32:22.880
How about you compose couplets

32:22.960 --> 32:24.640
and challenge the young ladies
to match them?

32:24.720 --> 32:27.320
If anyone succeeds,

32:27.400 --> 32:29.280
-they'll drink a toast.
-Sounds great!

32:29.360 --> 32:30.720
That's a great idea!

32:32.080 --> 32:33.480
Since you've proposed it,

32:33.560 --> 32:36.240
it would indeed be a privilege to witness
the young ladies' literary talents.

32:36.320 --> 32:39.840
Excellent. Young Master Wu,
why don't you start us off?

32:48.080 --> 32:49.600
Beside the wall lies Willow Alley.

32:49.680 --> 32:50.920
Water floods the long dike.

32:51.000 --> 32:53.240
Narrow paths make the cattle
doubt there's room to tread.

32:53.760 --> 32:54.600
Excellent!

32:55.480 --> 32:58.560
Your talent rivals those of the scholars
from the Imperial Academy!

33:24.840 --> 33:25.720
Ming.

33:29.040 --> 33:30.400
You can write…

33:42.080 --> 33:43.600
Dou Ming has written one.

33:44.520 --> 33:46.640
Beyond the heart lies Peach Blossom Land.

33:46.720 --> 33:48.000
Clouds obscure the narrow path

33:48.080 --> 33:51.200
In a forest where animals roam
a new world unfolds.

33:51.280 --> 33:52.680
Brilliant!

33:52.760 --> 33:54.880
What a perfect match!

34:01.520 --> 34:02.600
Thank you for the inspiration,
Young Master Wu.

34:07.960 --> 34:09.560
Shi Shu, look at this couplet.

34:12.560 --> 34:13.400
Here.

34:25.639 --> 34:27.600
Young Lady Ming completely
stole the spotlight.

34:27.679 --> 34:29.840
Wang Ying Xue must be overjoyed.

34:29.920 --> 34:32.800
-Why is she still dragging this on?
-Yes, why, Shou Gu?

34:32.880 --> 34:35.320
That's just how she is.

34:35.400 --> 34:37.239
Young Lady Zhao, you're very talented.

34:37.320 --> 34:38.840
Why haven't you written anything?

34:39.960 --> 34:42.159
I grew up in the countryside.
I'm not skilled in literature.

34:43.360 --> 34:44.800
You must be joking.

34:44.880 --> 34:46.840
The young ladies are
the stars of this banquet.

34:47.719 --> 34:49.639
Why don't you compose a couplet?

34:56.199 --> 34:58.640
Shou Gu, do you not want to write one?

34:58.720 --> 35:00.160
Let me write one for you then.

35:19.640 --> 35:22.880
A young boy herds sheep
and cattle in the northern plains,

35:22.960 --> 35:26.800
watching the sheep, the cattle,
and the stars.

35:29.240 --> 35:30.080
I have one to match that.

35:31.560 --> 35:34.760
A bandit in black sneaks in at midnight,

35:34.840 --> 35:39.040
grabbing, embracing, and stealing kisses.

35:47.040 --> 35:48.280
Shameless scoundrel.

35:54.240 --> 35:55.080
Outrageous!

35:55.160 --> 35:56.440
Judging by the handwriting,

35:57.080 --> 35:59.120
this must be from Young Lady Zhang Ru.

35:59.760 --> 36:02.040
Zhao Si is a two-time
imperial exam laureate,

36:02.680 --> 36:04.040
yet his only daughter comes up

36:04.560 --> 36:06.600
with something so vulgar and absurd.

36:07.440 --> 36:09.040
And you, Young Master Pang,
matched it so well.

36:09.800 --> 36:11.320
Shall I arrange a marriage for you

36:12.120 --> 36:14.720
to become the Zhao family's
live-in son-in-law?

36:14.800 --> 36:16.240
Who would want him as a husband?

36:16.880 --> 36:18.400
It was thoughtless
of me to speak like that.

36:19.640 --> 36:21.520
He thought it was written by Zhao.

36:21.600 --> 36:22.440
He was just trying to help her.

36:22.520 --> 36:24.280
It was just a joke.

36:24.360 --> 36:26.440
Young Lady Zhao's couplet
lacked refinement,

36:26.520 --> 36:27.840
so naturally, the reply was vulgar too.

36:28.480 --> 36:29.880
With her parents far away in Diannan,

36:30.520 --> 36:31.800
she's had no one to guide her.

36:31.880 --> 36:34.080
After years mingling with merchants
and common folk in the countryside,

36:34.160 --> 36:36.480
it's no surprise
she's neglected her studies.

36:36.560 --> 36:37.560
You're full of crap!

36:41.360 --> 36:42.400
Alright, alright.

36:42.920 --> 36:44.080
By your reasoning,

36:44.600 --> 36:47.000
I too grew up without parents' guidance,
doing lowly work

36:47.080 --> 36:48.840
-and mingling with country folk…
-Dou Zhao!

36:53.640 --> 36:55.960
You know what, I've thought of a couplet.

36:57.600 --> 36:58.880
Shou Gu!

37:00.000 --> 37:01.760
What is she doing here?

37:01.840 --> 37:03.800
Dou Zhao, this is the men's table.

37:03.880 --> 37:04.960
What are you doing?

37:05.040 --> 37:06.400
-Have you no shame?
-Dou Zhao…

37:11.680 --> 37:14.680
If you gentlemen can openly
discuss women's marriages

37:14.760 --> 37:15.840
without shame,

37:15.920 --> 37:16.760
why should I feel embarrassed?

37:21.360 --> 37:22.880
That folding fan is traditionally used

37:22.960 --> 37:24.320
only by courtesans or talented scholars.

37:25.200 --> 37:26.440
Young Master Liu Xue Zhen,

37:26.520 --> 37:28.800
I heard you've failed
the imperial exam six times.

37:28.880 --> 37:30.240
You're using a folding fan too,

37:30.320 --> 37:31.880
but where's the talent to match it?

37:34.280 --> 37:35.840
Young Lady Zhao, as a lady,

37:35.920 --> 37:38.200
talking like that is highly inappropriate.

37:38.280 --> 37:39.880
Young Master Chen Shi Yuan,

37:39.960 --> 37:41.080
I hear your family's business failed,

37:41.160 --> 37:42.440
and you even had
to sell your ancestral home.

37:43.040 --> 37:44.880
You're looking for a dowry to
make up for the losses, aren't you?

37:46.320 --> 37:48.000
Shou Gu has been away
from the capital for years.

37:48.080 --> 37:49.520
How does she know all that?

37:50.440 --> 37:51.560
EASY IT IS TO FIND A FICKLE LOVER
BUT PRICELESS TREASURES ARE HARD TO SEEK.

37:56.360 --> 37:58.520
Easy it is to find a fickle lover,

37:58.600 --> 38:00.520
but priceless treasures are hard to seek.

38:01.040 --> 38:04.800
Why waste false affection
on embroidered words?

38:05.440 --> 38:07.840
I can't stand men like you,

38:07.920 --> 38:08.960
talentless, unprincipled sycophants.

38:09.040 --> 38:11.720
Just because you're educated,
you think you're above everyone,

38:11.800 --> 38:12.880
criticizing and belittling women.

38:12.960 --> 38:15.320
You treat marriage like items
on a marketplace shelf,

38:15.400 --> 38:17.200
weighing and scheming over them.

38:18.240 --> 38:20.360
If we're the leftover
oranges and rotten sugarcane,

38:20.960 --> 38:22.880
-what are you? Flies and vermin?
-Insolent!

38:23.840 --> 38:25.280
You're behaving improperly

38:25.360 --> 38:28.160
and speaking nonsense
in front of our guests.

38:28.240 --> 38:29.600
Zhao is as impressive as usual.

38:30.120 --> 38:32.320
Young Master Wu, my apologies
for the spectacle.

38:32.400 --> 38:34.120
Young Lady Zhao's couplet

38:34.200 --> 38:35.160
is sincere and sharp-witted,

38:35.760 --> 38:37.560
with a touch of satirical humor.

38:38.080 --> 38:39.480
I don't find anything

38:40.000 --> 38:41.120
improper about them.

38:41.640 --> 38:45.200
Though I must admit, her couplet
is quite difficult to match.

38:46.040 --> 38:47.520
My behavior is crude

38:48.280 --> 38:49.880
and unworthy of your company.

38:50.400 --> 38:51.400
I'll excuse myself to reflect.

38:56.840 --> 38:58.560
We'll go with you!

38:59.280 --> 39:00.520
Let them go.

39:05.880 --> 39:07.560
Will Young Lady Zhao be bullied?

39:09.840 --> 39:13.240
In noble households, one must
act with careful timing.

39:14.280 --> 39:17.840
Being too sharp and outspoken
isn't always wise.

39:18.800 --> 39:23.160
The question is whether she can hold back.

39:23.880 --> 39:25.560
If she can,

39:26.120 --> 39:28.160
we'll need to wait about
half an incense stick's time.

39:28.240 --> 39:31.080
Mr. Chen, you always speak in riddles.

39:31.960 --> 39:33.840
And what if she can't conceal it?

39:34.440 --> 39:35.520
Zhao, please wait!

39:36.600 --> 39:37.440
They're out.

39:37.520 --> 39:40.040
Zhao, don't be mad.

39:40.120 --> 39:41.320
I'm not mad.

39:41.840 --> 39:43.840
It's not worth getting
angry over those people.

39:46.120 --> 39:48.880
Young Lady, are you really not mad?

39:48.960 --> 39:50.280
Fine, maybe I am a little mad.

39:51.320 --> 39:53.480
Mr. Chen, I understand
that you wanted me to come,

39:53.560 --> 39:54.960
hoping I'd learn to be patient.

39:57.600 --> 39:59.520
But this isn't entirely a bad thing.

40:00.160 --> 40:01.400
In official families,
when choosing a wife,

40:01.480 --> 40:03.840
they care most about virtue and obedience.

40:04.520 --> 40:07.640
If I earn myself a reputation
as a shrew or troublemaker,

40:08.160 --> 40:10.840
it'll give the Marquis of Jining a perfect
excuse to break off the engagement.

40:10.920 --> 40:12.600
That'll save me from
their constant pressure to marry.

40:12.680 --> 40:16.240
Zhao, do you really not care
about your reputation or marriage?

40:16.320 --> 40:18.880
Women can live perfectly well
without relying on men.

40:20.080 --> 40:23.160
Becoming someone's wife means
taking care of his parents,

40:23.680 --> 40:26.240
worrying about his career,
managing the household,

40:26.800 --> 40:28.880
and even looking after concubines
and their children.

40:29.400 --> 40:31.000
And if you really love him,

40:31.880 --> 40:33.600
you might end up like my mother.

40:37.000 --> 40:39.560
I still want to meet someone I love,

40:39.640 --> 40:40.560
get married, and have children.

40:41.400 --> 40:44.000
My parents weren't around
when I was growing up.

40:44.080 --> 40:46.360
I've always wanted a home.

40:46.440 --> 40:48.080
What about you, Zhang Ru?

40:51.120 --> 40:53.560
I'm going to beat those
uncultured brats right now!

40:53.640 --> 40:55.960
How dare they call me old,
crude, and unwanted!

40:56.040 --> 40:59.360
I'll show them what crudeness
really looks like!

40:59.440 --> 41:01.560
Zhang Ru, sit down. Sit.

41:01.640 --> 41:03.240
Oh, Zhang Ru.

41:03.760 --> 41:06.400
They are blind and ignorant.

41:06.480 --> 41:07.760
They can't see how amazing you are.

41:10.480 --> 41:13.400
That's right! If my father hadn't
insisted on a live-in son-in-law,

41:13.480 --> 41:14.960
I'd have been married long ago, right?

41:17.440 --> 41:18.960
Alright, she's had too much to drink.

41:19.040 --> 41:21.520
I'll take her back. Come on.

41:22.040 --> 41:24.360
I'm feeling stifled.
I'm going to take a walk.

41:24.440 --> 41:26.440
Alright. Don't stay out too late.

41:26.960 --> 41:27.840
Come on.

41:28.360 --> 41:30.680
-Su Su, drink with me.
-Alright, alright.

41:51.440 --> 41:53.880
Young Lady, we're being followed.

41:54.880 --> 41:56.200
Young Lady, have a look.

41:59.280 --> 42:01.680
Go back to Dou's Residence
and get some money.

42:01.760 --> 42:03.440
Yes, Young Lady.

42:11.320 --> 42:12.400
Goodbye.

42:18.960 --> 42:21.760
THE TALE OF THE SILKEN ROBE

42:21.840 --> 42:24.200
Good sir, we have a new performance,
The Tale of the Silken Robe.

42:24.280 --> 42:26.840
A lost mother, an abandoned child,
and a courtroom trial of the father.

42:26.920 --> 42:29.320
A life adrift, tangled with
love and resentment,

42:29.400 --> 42:31.080
and an unbreakable bond
between a father and a son.

42:31.600 --> 42:33.000
There are still seats available
in the private boxes.

42:33.080 --> 42:34.200
Please step inside.

42:35.880 --> 42:38.200
We have tea, snacks, everything you need.

42:47.480 --> 42:48.520
Please come in.

43:13.040 --> 43:15.240
When I invited Ji Jian Ming to our estate,

43:15.320 --> 43:17.640
it was to see if he and Shou Gu
might be a good match.

43:17.720 --> 43:19.720
Ji Jian Ming and Shou Gu
have been meeting in private.

43:19.800 --> 43:20.640
They're clearly in love.

43:21.240 --> 43:23.560
Zhao, how far have things
gone between you two?

43:23.640 --> 43:24.800
Watch out!

45:18.400 --> 45:19.600
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
DURING THE MAKING OF THIS FILM.

45:19.680 --> 45:21.240
MEDICAL ACTS AND DRUGS IN THIS DRAMA ARE
FICTIONAL. DO NOT IMITATE.
